A man and a woman have been arrested after an alleged serious assault in Paisley.&nbsp;The incident happened late on Monday May 11, at Blackstoun Oval in Ferguslie Park.A 23-year-old man and 35-year-old woman were taken to hospital after the alleged assault.Now a 30-year-old man and a 26-year-old woman have been arrested in connection with the incident, and a report will be sent to the Procurator Fiscal.The pair were due to appear at Paisley Sheriff Court on May 19.